# BETA.3 fix - migrations must be tracked for `prisma migrate deploy` to
# work at all. This line used to ignore server/prisma/migrations/ entirely,
# which silently discarded every migration folder (including the BETA.3
# baseline migration and its migration_lock.toml) - git status showed
# clean, nothing ever reached GitHub, and a stale local-only migration
# (20260629000001_init, predating the GROUP profile type) sat invisible on
# disk the whole time. Migrations now live in git like any other source
# file - see docs/product/CLOSED_BETA_GATE.md section 3.

